Tue Jul 30 01:44:02 2002  Tim Janik  <timj@gtk.org>

	* docs/generated/release-notes.dat: updates.

	* beast-gtk/bstplayback.[hc]: export API for seeking.

	* beast-gtk/bstwaveeditor.[hc]: add seek scale.

